    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/5559ebfedeadb30253904bf6d37c7529.poster.avif?t=1770404875\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/5559ebfedeadb30253904bf6d37c7529.webm?t=1770404875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/5559ebfedeadb30253904bf6d37c7529.mp4?t=1770404875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fishing Valley is a captivating 2D simulation-adventure game set in a picturesque world of the open ocean and bustling havens. Begin your journey as a novice angler with basic equipment and a modest boat. Complete a variety of fishing tasks, each designed to challenge your skills and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/bdb4cc662f5739714577128af626a87e.avif?t=1770404875\" width=616 height=80 /></span>Embark on missions to catch specific fish species, utilizing quick time events to reel in your catch. Each successful mission unlocks new items and havens, offering fresh challenges and opportunities to explore diverse environments. Whether navigating tranquil waters or bustling fishing docks, each location is beautifully rendered with unique art and atmospheric details.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/ed9788d045ec73b2cdc295dfb452cba3.poster.avif?t=1770404875\" width=614 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/ed9788d045ec73b2cdc295dfb452cba3.webm?t=1770404875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/ed9788d045ec73b2cdc295dfb452cba3.mp4?t=1770404875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/3db24cf948bc76a2144b1c1d0dbb89c2.avif?t=1770404875\" width=616 height=80 /></span>Fish freely in open waters, selling your catch to earn money, or add it to your customizable aquarium, which you can decorate with various items. Use your earnings to upgrade your fishing gear and boat, enhancing your abilities and unlocking advanced equipment. The game's immersive story-driven approach keeps you engaged as you uncover new quests and narrative elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/74e09ef105dd927eef97ed0cf6f510a5.poster.avif?t=1770404875\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/74e09ef105dd927eef97ed0cf6f510a5.webm?t=1770404875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/74e09ef105dd927eef97ed0cf6f510a5.mp4?t=1770404875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/11ceed1590bcb097a0dd532f7a8f5cad.avif?t=1770404875\" width=616 height=80 /></span>Experience the joy of angling in &quot;Fishing Valley,&quot; where every catch brings new rewards and every adventure unfolds a new chapter in your fishing saga. Customize your approach, adapt to varying fishing conditions, and immerse yourself in a vibrant world where fishing is both an art and a thrilling adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/f08472ddd0eec98e14042de6f5302df4.avif?t=1770404875\" width=616 height=80 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 30 Fish Species</strong>: Catch over 30 unique species of fish, with more to be added in future updates.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/c67a59169b41b6eea06814ce0f0b1943.avif?t=1770404875\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Engaging Missions</strong>: Complete specific tasks to catch various fish and unlock new quests.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick Time Events</strong>: Experience dynamic fishing through quick time events, adding excitement and challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character Customization</strong>: Customize your character and purchase a variety of hats to personalize your look.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/d916c905275fe0b237d59e2c9cd3e595.avif?t=1770404875\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Havens</strong>: Discover different havens, each with its own set of challenges and fish species.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free Fishing Mode</strong>: Fish freely and sell your catch to earn money or add it to your customizable aquarium.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable Aquarium</strong>: Decorate your aquarium with various items, showcasing your prized catches.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3137840/extras/77253a2d0ea72f8955d938ef9d98027a.avif?t=1770404875\" width=616 height=140 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgradable Equipment</strong>: Use earned money to upgrade your fishing gear and boat for better performance.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story-Driven Experience</strong>: Enjoy a narrative-driven adventure with beautiful art and immersive storytelling.</p></li></ul>",
